text:
[Verse]
Stars up in the sky
Shine bright you and I
Dream beyond the lights
Glow in endless nights

[Verse 2]
Moonlight on the sea
Dancing wild and free
Whispers in the dark
Love's a spark
A mark

[Chorus]
Starry night hold me tight
Underneath the cosmic light
We can fly love can guide
Through the skies side by side

[Verse 3]
Waves crash on the shore
Promises and more
Hearts that feel so deep
Secrets we both keep

[Bridge]
Midnight signals play
In the Milky Way
Falling stars we see
Just you and me

[Chorus]
Starry night hold me tight
Underneath the cosmic light
We can fly love can guide
Through the skies side by side
title: Starry Night
